{
  "stem": "27340.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody was smoking in those days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was a very grim experience, a beaten army, because that's what they were, terribly bedraggled, many of them with head wounds and bandages and so on and so forth, many who had to be helped ashore by colleagues, many of them with hardly any uniform left.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were quite a lot of-- of top half at least naked soldiers coming on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were so demoralized that I remember they took their steel helmets and their First World War rifles, Lee-Enfields, and threw those into the sea as a sign of disgust and total abjection.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was lighting cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because at the age of 13 I was not an experienced smoker and cigarettes were not as sophisticated as they are today with tips, the-- my-- the skin on my lips were very, very raw, because with every cigarette there went a little bit of my skin on the cigarette into the soldier's mouth.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this went on for about three days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I must have got through, oh, easily one-and-a-half-thousand cigarettes of so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And my lips were incredibly raw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But you know, this was part of the war effort.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We all had to make a sacrifice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I wasn't particularly worried about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the end, you know, it all righted itself, obviously.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My introduction to cigarettes, we were then very shortly afterwards evacuated, because by that time, the hostel was in a sad state.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had no windows left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were all blown out by bomb blasts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were never hit directly by a bomb, but the Germans naturally were trying to hamper the retreat as much as they possibly could.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so they bombed harbor installations and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
